Mod-NTCdrive
=======

> [Datasheet](https://docs.google.com/document/d/1xpLEcBNHOzufufisoClGkodkMlKaTpSObjkInAdEXmk/export?format=pdf) üìú

Add the ability to measure NTC temperature to your hardware application with a fully digital interface.

#### Summary ‚ÑπÔ∏è

*   Any 10K NTC 
*   Resolution 0.125 ¬∞C
*   I¬≤C interface
